song.title: Doctor Destiny
song.info:
Chanel5 strikes again with another crappy punk rock, listen it at your own risk. (lol)
Entry for multichannel compo at Assembly '95, I regret everything.. I regret everything that I've ever done why I uploaded this piece of crap.

Hahahaaa. This song sucks, woohoo. Let's kick some aaaaasss!
There's no light, there's always dark There's too dark, I have to fart If I asked you, would you show the way or should I just... DRIIIIIIFT AWAAAAAAY! *wah*
Shoot yourself, you were innocent Anarchy has caused another accident
One, two, three! Kill then me, kill da Doctor Destiny! (^ and then it repeats this part all over to the end)
